quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  89,24,"yqwl: ya laytani qddamt fi aldunya min al'aemal ma ynfeny lihayati fi alakhrt"
  89,25,"ffy dhlk alyawm aleasib la yastatie ahd wala yuqadar 'ana yuedhdhib mithl taedhib allah min esah, wala yastatie 'ahad 'an ywthiq mithl wthaq allh, wala yablugh ahd mblghh fi dhlk"
  89,26,"ffy dhlk alyawm aleasib la yastatie ahd wala yuqadar 'ana yuedhdhib mithl taedhib allah min esah, wala yastatie 'ahad 'an ywthiq mithl wthaq allh, wala yablugh ahd mblghh fi dhlk"
  89,27,"ya 'ayatuha alnafs almutmayinat 'iilaa dhikr allah wal'iiman bh, wabima aeddah min alnaeim llmwmnyn, arjiei 'iilaa rabik radiatan b'ikram allah lk, wallah subhanah qad radi enk, fadkhuli fi eidad eibad allah alsalhyn, wadkhuli maeahum jnty"
  89,28,"ya 'ayatuha alnafs almutmayinat 'iilaa dhikr allah wal'iiman bh, wabima aeddah min alnaeim llmwmnyn, arjiei 'iilaa rabik radiatan b'ikram allah lk, wallah subhanah qad radi enk, fadkhuli fi eidad eibad allah alsalhyn, wadkhuli maeahum jnty"
  89,29,"ya 'ayatuha alnafs almutmayinat 'iilaa dhikr allah wal'iiman bh, wabima aeddah min alnaeim llmwmnyn, arjiei 'iilaa rabik radiatan b'ikram allah lk, wallah subhanah qad radi enk, fadkhuli fi eidad eibad allah alsalhyn, wadkhuli maeahum jnty"
  89,30,"ya 'ayatuha alnafs almutmayinat 'iilaa dhikr allah wal'iiman bh, wabima aeddah min alnaeim llmwmnyn, arjiei 'iilaa rabik radiatan b'ikram allah lk, wallah subhanah qad radi enk, fadkhuli fi eidad eibad allah alsalhyn, wadkhuli maeahum jnty"
  90,1,"aqsm allah bhdha albalad alhram, wahu \"mk\", wa'ant -ayha alnby- muqim fi hadha \"albld alhram\", waqsm bwald albshryt- wahu adam ealayh alslam- wama tnasl minh min wld, laqad khalaqna al'iinsan fi shdt wena' min mkabdt aldnya"
  90,2,"aqsm allah bhdha albalad alhram, wahu \"mk\", wa'ant -ayha alnby- muqim fi hadha \"albld alhram\", waqsm bwald albshryt- wahu adam ealayh alslam- wama tnasl minh min wld, laqad khalaqna al'iinsan fi shdt wena' min mkabdt aldnya"
  90,3,"aqsm allah bhdha albalad alhram, wahu \"mk\", wa'ant -ayha alnby- muqim fi hadha \"albld alhram\", waqsm bwald albshryt- wahu adam ealayh alslam- wama tnasl minh min wld, laqad khalaqna al'iinsan fi shdt wena' min mkabdt aldnya"
  90,4,"aqsm allah bhdha albalad alhram, wahu \"mk\", wa'ant -ayha alnby- muqim fi hadha \"albld alhram\", waqsm bwald albshryt- wahu adam ealayh alslam- wama tnasl minh min wld, laqad khalaqna al'iinsan fi shdt wena' min mkabdt aldnya"
  90,5,ayznn bima jameah min maal 'ana allah lan yaqdir elyh?
  90,6,"yaqul mtbahyana: 'unfiqat malana kthyrana. ayznn fi faealah hdha 'ana allah eaza wajala la yrah, wala yhasbh ealaa alsaghir walkbyr?"
  90,7,"yqwl mtbahyana: 'unfiqat malana kthyrana. ayznn fi faealah hdha 'ana allah eaza wajala la yrah, wala yhasbh ealaa alsaghir walkbyr?"
  90,8,"alm najeal lah eaynayn yubsir bhma, wlsanana washafatayn yantiq bha, wbynna lah sbylay alkhayr walshr?"
  90,9,"alm najeal lah eaynayn yubsir bhma, wlsanana washafatayn yantiq bha, wbynna lah sbylay alkhayr walshr?"
  90,10,"alm najeal lah eaynayn yubsir bhma, wlsanana washafatayn yantiq bha, wbynna lah sbylay alkhayr walshr?"
  90,11,"fhla tajawuz mshqt alakhirat bi'iinfaq malh, fyamn"
  90,12,"way shay' aelmk: ma mshqt alakhrt, wama yueayin ealaa tjawzha?"
  90,13,'inh etq raqabat muwminat man 'asara alrriq
  90,14,"aw 'iiteam fi yawm dhi mjaet shdydt, ytymana min dhwy alqarabat yajtamie fih fadal alsdqt wslt alrhm, 'aw fqyrana medmana la shay' endh"
  90,15,"aw 'iiteam fi yawm dhi mjaet shdydt, ytymana min dhwy alqarabat yajtamie fih fadal alsdqt wslt alrhm, 'aw fqyrana medmana la shay' endh"
  90,16,"aw 'iiteam fi yawm dhi mjaet shdydt, ytymana min dhwy alqarabat yajtamie fih fadal alsdqt wslt alrhm, 'aw fqyrana medmana la shay' endh"
  90,17,"thm kan mae fiel ma dhukr min 'aemal alkhayr min aladhin akhlsu al'iiman llh, wa'awsaa baeduhum bedana bialsabr ealaa taeat allah waean measyh, watawasawa balrhmt balkhlq"
  90,18,"aldhyn faealuu hadhih alafeal, hum 'ashab alymyn, aladhin yukhadh bihim yawm alqiamat dhat alyamin 'iilaa aljnt"
  90,19,waldhyn kafaruu bialquran hum aladhin yukhadh bihim yawm alqiamat dhat alshimal 'iilaa alnar
  90,20,jzawhm jahanam mtbaqt mughlaqatan elyhm